Empty string

{{task}} 

Languages may have features for dealing specifically with empty strings 
(those containing no characters).


;Task:
::* &nbsp; Demonstrate how to assign an empty string to a variable.
::* &nbsp; Demonstrate how to check that a string is empty.
::* &nbsp; Demonstrate how to check that a string is not empty.
<br><br>

[[Category:String manipulation]] [[Category:Simple]]


=={{header|JavaScript}}==
Create an empty String
<lang javascript>var s = "";
var s = new String();</lang>

Boolean expressions representing emptiness
<lang javascript>s == ""
s.length == 0
!s
!Boolean(s)</lang>

Non-emptiness
<lang javascript>!!s
s != ""
s.length != 0
s.length > 0
Boolean(s)</lang>

